. *--- Paso 1: Varianza residual → sigma2 para corrección B-O
. predict resid_vec, equation(#1) residuals
(4 missing values generated)

. qui summarize resid_vec if train==1

. scalar sigma2_vec = r(Var)

. drop resid_vec

